## 3. Full GNN Pipeline Replacing GDS Workflow

```
Neo4j (storage + Cypher)
      │
      │  MATCH (n)-[r]->(m) RETURN ...
      ▼
NetworkX / igraph (Python)
      │
      │  Classical algorithms (fast, exact)
      │  PageRank, WCC, Louvain, Betweenness
      ▼
PyTorch Geometric (PyG)
      │
      │  GNN training (node2vec, GCN, GraphSAGE, GAT)
      │  Node classification, link prediction
      ▼
Results (embeddings, labels, scores)
      │
      │  UNWIND $results MATCH (n) SET n.score = ...
      ▼
Neo4j (write results back via Cypher)
```

### Complete Pipeline Code
```python
import networkx as nx
import community as community_louvain
from node2vec import Node2Vec
from neo4j import GraphDatabase
import pandas as pd

driver = GraphDatabase.driver("bolt://localhost:7687", auth=("neo4j", "password"))

# 1. Extract graph
G = neo4j_to_networkx(driver, "Person", "KNOWS")
G_undirected = G.to_undirected()

# 2. Classical algorithms
pagerank = nx.pagerank(G, alpha=0.85)
communities = community_louvain.best_partition(G_undirected)
wcc = {n: i for i, comp in enumerate(nx.weakly_connected_components(G))
       for n in comp}

# 3. Node embeddings
node2vec = Node2Vec(G, dimensions=64, walk_length=30, num_walks=10, workers=2)
model = node2vec.fit(window=5, min_count=1)

# 4. Build feature DataFrame
results = []
for node in G.nodes():
    results.append({
        "node_id": node,
        "pagerank": pagerank[node],
        "community": communities.get(node, -1),
        "component": wcc[node],
        "embedding": model.wv[str(node)].tolist()
    })
df = pd.DataFrame(results)

# 5. Write back to Neo4j
with driver.session() as session:
    session.run("""
        UNWIND $rows AS row
        MATCH (n) WHERE id(n) = row.node_id
        SET n.pagerank = row.pagerank,
            n.community = row.community,
            n.component = row.component
    """, rows=df[["node_id","pagerank","community","component"]].to_dict("records"))

print("Pipeline complete:", df.shape)
```

